## **PHASE 5: Sales Order with Plafond Control (NEW)**

### **Plafond Management:**
- Customer punya limit kredit (misal 10 juta)
- Plafond_used = total SO yang belum dibayar
- Threshold warning di 95% (5% buffer)
- Saat plafond_used >= 100% → SO blocked (tidak bisa create)
- Saat invoice dibayar → plafond_used berkurang, SO bisa dibuat lagi

### **B2B vs B2C Pricing:**
- **B2C**: Pakai harga default dari master product
- **B2B**: Harga bisa custom per customer
  - Disimpan di table `customer_product_pricing` (customer_id, product_id, custom_price)
  - Sales set manual saat create SO (no approval needed)
  - Pilihan: **Overwrite** (update master pricing) atau **Keep in SO only** (hanya di SO line item)
  - Next SO untuk customer B2B yang sama → Harga custom sudah tersimpan

### **Sales Order Flow:**
1. Sales pilih customer (B2B/B2C)
2. Cek plafond status → Show warning badge jika >95%
3. Jika plafond full → Block SO creation
4. Saat add product ke SO:
   - B2C → Auto-fill harga default
   - B2B → Auto-fill custom price (jika ada), atau default (jika belum ada)
5. Sales bisa override harga di SO line item
6. Saat SO confirmed → Opsi save custom price ke master atau keep di SO saja

